project_descr: Support to stabilisation, socio-economic recovery and prevention of radicalization of vulnerable populations through access to employment and social services in conflict-affected communities

outputs.output_descr: Populations and communities in Bangui, Bossangoa and Bambari affected by the conflict  become less resilient to outside and inside shocks and outbreaks of violence. social cohesion fabric, community security and livelihood means needs support.

project_title: support to stabilisation and socio-economic recovery
